======================== #create user using jenkins dashboard#========================
1. Go to Manage Jenkins > Manage Users > Create User
2. Fill in the user details and click Create User
3. The new user will be created and can be used to log in to Jenkins

#now assign roles to the user
1. Go to Manage Jenkins > plugin Manager > Available > role based authorization strategy >install
2. After installation, go to Manage Jenkins > Security > Authorization > Role-Based Strategy > Save
3. Go to Manage Jenkins > Manage and Assign Roles > Manage Roles
4. Create a new role (e.g., "role1") and assign permissions
5. Go to Manage Jenkins > Manage and Assign Roles > Assign Roles
6. Assign the created role to the user
7. Save the changes
# The user now has the assigned roles and permissions

